## ▓▒░ The Grimoire ░▒▓

> *"In the abyss of raw data, I find the patterns others cannot see."*

I am a first-year IT student at **National University Fairview** — scholar, builder, and practitioner of the dark arts of data. By day I attend lectures. By night I write Rust smart contracts, wrangle datasets, and conjure pipelines from the void.

Currently pursuing a path in **data analytics and data engineering** with the tools of the modern age: SQL, Python, AWS, and Stellar blockchain.

