## ▓▒░ Conjured Works ░▒▓

### ⛓ ScholarChain PH
> *On-chain scholarship disbursement for Filipino students*

A Stellar blockchain dApp built with **Rust + Soroban smart contracts**, deployed to Stellar Testnet. Credential verification and scholarship disbursement, immutable and transparent.

```
Contract: CCYASD3OJXWDSUMCLOQ246JB62DJAR6CABZZOLIHR7VG5YOQ3NPLEL5S
Built for: Stellar Philippines UniTour 2026 · Rise In Bootcamp
